query:
SELECT 
  COUNT(*) as total_records,
  SUM(CASE WHEN prefecture IS NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as null_prefecture,
  SUM(CASE WHEN city IS NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as null_city,
  SUM(CASE WHEN avg_price_per_sqm IS NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as null_avg_price,
  SUM(CASE WHEN transaction_count IS NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as null_transaction_count
FROM aggregated_real_estate_data;
